551
00:44:33,767 --> 00:44:36,333
What a roller coaster that was yesterday.

552
00:44:40,066 --> 00:44:42,033
Today, another game begins.

553
00:44:43,033 --> 00:44:45,800
The genius shogi player, Akira Mori,

554
00:44:45,867 --> 00:44:49,667
