568
00:45:41,834 --> 00:45:44,166
To shoot or not to shoot.

569
00:45:44,233 --> 00:45:45,066
YUKI VS SENYA

570
00:45:45,767 --> 00:45:48,667
There's only one thing she can do.
Win the game.

571
00:45:48,734 --> 00:45:50,000
Jump!

